Package: multiCure
Title: Multivariate Cure‐Rate Estimation and Testing
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhenyu", "Xu", , "zhenyu.xu@uconn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides estimation and hypothesis-testing tools for cure rates
  in multivariate survival data.  Supports two-sample (paired and independent)
  and K-sample Wald-type tests, covariance-weighted and simple-average 
  estimators, pooled Kaplan–Meier cure probabilities, and Ying–Wei variance 
  adjustments.
